<div style="position:absolute;left:187.10px;top:144.98px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">GUIDELINES FOR STUDENT-TRAINEES</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.00px;top:172.58px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">Dear Student-Trainee:</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:200.18px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">You are now ready to go to your respective training station. While you are in your training station,</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.00px;top:213.98px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">please observe these guidelines. They are intended for your protection and worthwhile stay in the company/</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.00px;top:227.78px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">agency.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:255.41px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">1.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:255.41px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Follow all rules and regulations of the company/ agency regarding the training program.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:283.01px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">2.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:283.01px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Maintain the good image of the University while in the company/ agency through your work</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:296.81px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">performance and courteous attitude towards the personnel.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:324.41px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">3.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:324.41px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Promote a good relationship between the University and training station.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:352.01px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">4.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:352.01px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Stick to your work assignment and never leave the company/ agency without the knowledge and</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:365.81px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">sanction of the University.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:393.41px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">5.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:393.41px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Communicate with your Faculty-in-Charge and/ or the Director of the IRJP on problems encountered</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:407.21px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">while on training for providing relevant and factual information.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:434.83px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">6.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:434.83px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Accomplish IRJP Form regarding industrial activities on a day to day basis and submit such reports at</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:448.63px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">the end of the month to your Faculty-in-Charge.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:476.23px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">7.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:476.23px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Secure from the company/ agency your Certificate of Completion of training at the end of training</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:490.03px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">program.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:517.63px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">8.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:517.63px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Immediately  one  week  after  the  training,  submit  to  your  Faculty-in-Charge  the  following</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:531.43px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">requirements.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:559.03px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">a. IRJP form for Daily Work Activities</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:572.83px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">b. Evaluation Sheet</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:586.63px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">c. Certificate of Completion</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.02px;top:600.46px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">d. Narrative Report</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:628.06px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">9.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:628.06px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Attend the post training as schedule after your training period.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:655.66px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">10. Good Luck and Happy Training.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:684.10px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">•</span><span class="cls_006"> </span><span class="cls_003">  Failure in my part to submit in due time these requirements will mean no credit and will be required to</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:697.90px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">repeat the program.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.00px;top:712.54px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">•</span><span class="cls_006"> </span><span class="cls_003">  Failure on my part to report during the deployment period will mean that I will be dropped and will</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.02px;top:726.34px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">repeat SIT in the succeeding semester.</span></div>
